      • ResolveRecord

        public ResolveRecord(Map<String,Object> map,
                     int recNum)
        Construct a new ResolveRecord from the passed-in map. This map is assumed to have been returned from the getExtendedFiles method; other maps will probably not work. The recNum parameter is used to tell the constructor which resolve rec to extract. If map is null and / or recNum is negative, this is equivalent to calling the default constructor.
